_sText:
My finished version of Jamess Battle Arena Beta

http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/115625

Anyway so in this version ive changed a few things.

1.Changed water texture to much nicer one.

2.Hightened most of the building for more realistic effect.

3.Changed the map textures to Citadel textures which look alot nicer now.

4.Added barriers on each side so you can take some cover from the large amount of gunfire that will be going on.

Thats it I think so enjoy and please rate.
